title: Person Of Interest - Still [EDR002]
author: Thijn
description:
Person Of Interest - Still [EDR002]

South Florida's very own J. Albert and Person of Interest come together for Exotic Dance Records on this four-track 12" of certified heat! B2 track "Still" made an appearance in last year's Bronze/Palace Paramount video and here provides a nice finisher to Exotic Dance's inaugural 12".

Available for sale now at your favourite online record stores.
